I am currently studying Computer Science at the University Of Portsmouth. I
own an A4000 060, PicassoIV, CDR and a nice big 17" monitor as well as lots of
other stuff. I am currently working on a software driver for Warp3D, the
Amigas 3D graphics standard.

I enjoy listening to Pulp while I program in C (SAS) and Assembler (Devpac3).

